---

<BaseLayout
  title="Architectural Review – First Ballston Commons"
  description="Submit exterior changes for First Ballston Commons with the Architectural Review application and guidelines for updates and repairs."
  canonical="/architectural-review"
>
  <NavBar />

  <section class="hero-image relative overflow-hidden pt-20 text-white">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/60 via-black/25 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-14 md:py-20">
      <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl leading-tight font-extrabold md:text-5xl">Architectural Review</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/90">
          How to get exterior changes approved while keeping First Ballston Commons cohesive and
          well maintained.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="bg-background-light grow">
    <section class="py-12">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
        <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr]">
          <article
            class="space-y-10 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm md:p-10"
          >
            <section class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">
                <span
                  class="bg-primary flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-sm font-semibold text-white"
                  >1</span
                >
                Understanding the process
              </h3>
              <div class="space-y-4 leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
                <p class="m-0">
                  To keep First Ballston Commons cohesive, exterior changes must be reviewed and
                  approved by the Architectural Review Committee before work begins.
                </p>
                <p class="m-0">This includes, but is not limited to:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc space-y-2 pl-6 text-slate-700">
                  <li>Window or sliding door replacements (including trim)</li>
                  <li>Front door or storm door changes</li>
                  <li>Painting shutters, doors, or trim a new color</li>
                  <li>Fence replacement</li>
                </ul>
                <div
                  class="border-primary rounded-r-xl border-l-4 bg-blue-50 p-4 text-sm text-slate-700"
                >
                  <strong class="mb-1 block text-slate-900">Note</strong>
                  Routine maintenance that keeps the same appearance (for example, repainting with an
                  already approved color) usually does not need a full review. If you are unsure, please
                  ask before starting.
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">
                <span
                  class="bg-primary flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-sm font-semibold text-white"
                  >2</span
                >
                Submit your request
              </h3>
              <div class="space-y-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
                <p class="m-0 leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
                  Ready to start your project? Download the Architectural Approval Form, complete
                  every section, add samples or brochures, and send it to the association
                  management.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
                  <a
                    class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark inline-flex flex-1 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-white shadow transition"
                    href="/assets/architectural-approval-form.pdf"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener"
                  >
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">download</span>
                    Download request form
                  </a>
                  <a
                    class="inline-flex flex-1 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-800 transition hover:bg-slate-50"
                    href="https://engage.goenumerate.com/s/firstballstoncommons/hoapage.php?page=contact_17941"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener"
                  >
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">send</span>
                    Email application
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section class="space-y-4" id="approved-colors">
              <h3 class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">
                Approved Front Door Colors
              </h3>
              <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
                The following Benjamin Moore colors have been pre-approved for front doors. Submit
                an application for record keeping when selecting one of these hues.
              </p>
              <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4">
                {
                  approvedColors.map((color) => (
                    <a
                      href={color.link}
                      class="block h-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white text-slate-900 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg"
                      target="_blank"
                      rel="noopener"
                    >
                      <div class="h-36 w-full rounded-t-xl" style={`background: ${color.swatch}`} />
                      <div class="space-y-1 p-4">
                        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold">{color.name}</h3>
                        <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Benjamin Moore · Color Preview</div>
                        <div class="font-semibold">{color.code}</div>
                      </div>
                    </a>
                  ))
                }
              </div>
            </section>
          </article>

          <aside class="space-y-6">
            <div class="space-y-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span
                  class="bg-primary/10 text-primary inline-flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full"
                >
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">help</span>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="m-0 text-lg font-semibold">Need help?</h3>
                  <p class="m-0 text-sm text-slate-600">Ask questions before starting work</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <a
                  class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-white shadow transition"
                  href="https://engage.goenumerate.com/s/firstballstoncommons/hoapage.php?page=contact_17941"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener"
                >
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">forum</span>
                  Contact community manager
                </a>
                <a
                  class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-800 transition hover:bg-slate-50"
                  href="/assets/architectural-approval-form.pdf"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener"
                >
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">picture_as_pdf</span>
                  Architectural form
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-xl border border-dashed border-slate-300 bg-slate-50 p-4">
                <h4 class="mb-1 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Tip for faster approvals</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">
                  Include clear photos, paint swatches, and contractor details in a single packet so
                  the committee has everything it needs on the first review.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </aside>
